flowchart LR
  Agent[Agent core]:::agent
  subgraph STM["Short-term memory"]
    direction TB
    W[Working buffer]:::stm
    A[Session anchor]:::stm
  end
  subgraph LTM["Long-term memory"]
    direction TB
    V[(Vector store: tiered records)]:::ltm
    F[(Files: OKF md)]:::ltm
  end

  Agent -->|recent turns| W
  Agent -->|current task + next step| A
  Agent -->|store durable learnings| V
  Agent -->|write OKF records| F
  W -->|optional summary| V
  V -->|find: top-k relevant slice| Agent
  F -->|keyword recall| Agent
  A -->|self-repair after compaction| Agent

  classDef agent fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04,color:#422006;
  classDef stm fill:#ecfeff,stroke:#06b6d4,color:#083344;
  classDef ltm fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#052e16;
